text:
Storm Doris hits the UK – in pictures Share on Facebook Share on Twitter Share via Email View more sharing options Share on LinkedIn Share on Pinterest Share on Google+ Share on WhatsApp Share on Messenger Close 
The storm has brought snow and winds of up to 90mph to parts of Britain, causing travel disruption. Follow events in our live blog 
Ruff weather: have your pets been affected by Storm Doris? Contribute here Joanna Ruck
